This is a set of 'Reusable' tools created for specific purposes. 

Below is a list of tools (in sub-directories) that are part of this repository. 

- tempAlarm : A script that warns the user when temperature reaches a critical range (range is set by the user).
- 2csv : This converts the values separated by newline characters (in a file) into a single line of Comma-separated value.
- scrap : A tool to accumulate content from various places into a single image.

